'''2020年美国网球公开赛'''是第140届[[美国网球公开赛|美国网球公开赛]]，也是2020年的第二项[[大滿貫_(網球)|大满贯]]赛事，由[[國際網球總會|國際網球總會]]負責举办。本屆美國網球公開賽於8月31日至9月13日在[[纽约|纽约市]]的[[美國網球協會比莉·珍·金網球中心|美國網球協會比莉·珍·金網球中心]]室外[[硬地球場|硬地球场]]举行。

该比赛原本是2020年的第四项及最后一项网球大满贯赛事。然而受[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]][[2019冠状病毒病疫情|疫情]]影响，该年的[[法国网球公开赛|法国网球公开赛]]延期至9月底至10月进行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theweek.in/news/sports/2020/06/18/french-open-postponed-by-another-week-to-start-on-sep-27-with-fans.html|title=French Open postponed by another week, to start on Sep 27 with fans|publisher=The Week|date=2020-06-18|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629074044/https://www.theweek.in/news/sports/2020/06/18/french-open-postponed-by-another-week-to-start-on-sep-27-with-fans.html|archivedate=2020-06-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而原定于同年6月至7月进行的第134届[[温布尔登网球锦标赛|温布尔登网球锦标赛]]则取消举办<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wimbledon.com/en_GB/news/articles/2020-04-01/cancellation_of_the_championships_2020.html|title=Cancellation of The Championships 2020|work=The Championships, Wimbledon|date=2020-04-01|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231070314/https://www.wimbledon.com/en_GB/news/articles/2020-04-01/cancellation_of_the_championships_2020.html|archivedate=2020-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管美国为截至2020年8月[[2019冠狀病毒病美國疫情|确诊2019冠状病毒病人数最多的国家]]（按各国家和地区公开数字计算）<!--一定要强调公开数字，受检测及医疗资源有限之影响，全球可能有大量人士感染了病毒但却未能成为确诊病例-->，美国网球公开赛的主办方仍决定该届比赛在原计划的日期进行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/sport/tennis/us-open-safety-plans-on-track|title=US Open safety plans 'on track'|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2020-08-02|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809001605/https://www.straitstimes.com/sport/tennis/us-open-safety-plans-on-track|archivedate=2020-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

尽管预定举办的日期保持不变，赛事主办方仍针对此次疾病大流行出台了一些应对措施。观众方面，本次比赛[[無觀眾比賽|不设现场观众]]，这在美国网球公开赛乃至网球四大满贯赛历史尚属首次<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/06/sports/tennis/us-open-novak-djokovic.html|title=Novak Djokovic Out of U.S. Open After Accidental Hit of Line Judge|publisher=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911135635/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/06/sports/tennis/us-open-novak-djokovic.html|archivedate=2020-09-11|accessdate=2020-09-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>；项目设置方面，该届比赛的单打项目资格赛、成年组混合双打比赛和青年组比赛均被取消，成年健全组的男子双打及女子双打参赛组合数各自由64对减至32对；运动员方面，参赛选手必须在主办方指定的酒店居住，在除比赛、训练等以外的场合戴上口罩，及按要求接受[[2019冠状病毒病检测|病毒检测]]，检测结果阳性的选手必须放弃参加比赛，而与病毒检测阳性人士有密切接触的选手也必须放弃比赛并接受隔离<ref>{{cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/us-open-players-pulled-tournament-contact-covid-positive/story?id=72842299|title=US Open players pulled from tournament after contact with COVID-positive player|publisher=ABC News|date=2020-09-06|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200912093921/https://abcnews.go.com/US/us-open-players-pulled-tournament-contact-covid-positive/story?id=72842299|archivedate=2020-09-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref name="USOpen2020">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/tennis/53070667|title=US Open to be held behind closed doors after New York governor gives go-ahead|publisher=[[BBC体育|BBC Sport]]|date=2020-06-16|accessdate=2020-06-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702223153/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/tennis/53070667|archivedate=2020-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

主办方原定取消轮椅组的比赛，然而该决定遭到[[Dylan_Alcott|Dylan Alcott]]等选手的批评，认为此举是歧视残疾选手，最终主办方决定保留轮椅组比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-06-25/us-open-u-turn-on-wheelchair-tennis-after-dylan-alcott-blast/12390502|title=Wheelchair tennis back on at US Open after initial decision criticised by players including Dylan Alcott|publisher=ABC News Australia|date=2020-06-25|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626202840/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-06-25/us-open-u-turn-on-wheelchair-tennis-after-dylan-alcott-blast/12390502|archivedate=2020-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

尽管主办方制定应对措施以防止感染扩大。仍有不少选手因为安全相关的缘故决定放弃参加比赛，这当中包括上届[[2019年美國網球公開賽男子單打比賽|男单]]冠军[[拉斐爾·拿度|拉斐爾·拿度]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/2020/08/04/rafael-nadal-us-open/|title=Rafael Nadal bows out of U.S. Open, citing travel concerns amid pandemic|publisher=The Washington Post|date=2020-08-05|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911212039/https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/2020/08/04/rafael-nadal-us-open/|archivedate=2020-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>、上届[[2019年美國網球公開賽女子單打比賽|女单]]冠军[[比安卡·安德列絲庫|比安卡·安德列絲庫]]、女子单打世界排名第一的[[阿什莉·巴蒂|阿什莉·巴蒂]]、女子单打世界排名第二的[[西莫娜·哈勒普|西莫娜·哈勒普]]等。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/tennis/news/us-open-2020-a-complete-list-of-stars-who-have-withdrawn-from-tournament/|title=US Open 2020: A complete list of stars who have withdrawn from tournament|publisher=CBS Sports|date=2020-08-17|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200913105248/https://www.cbssports.com/tennis/news/us-open-2020-a-complete-list-of-stars-who-have-withdrawn-from-tournament/|archivedate=2020-09-13}}</ref>

该届比赛的总奖金为53,402,000[[美元|美元]]，与上届相比减少5%以上。各阶段奖金方面，除单打第二轮和第三轮及双打三十二强、十六强和八强奖金和上届持平外，其余阶段奖金均与上届相比有所减少。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usopen.org/en_US/news/articles/2020-08-05/usta_reaffirms_commitment_to_player_relief_efforts_with_2020_us_open_prize_money.html|title=USTA reaffirms commitment to player relief efforts with 2020 US Open prize money|work=US Open|date=2020-08-18|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827093440/https://www.usopen.org/en_US/news/articles/2020-08-05/usta_reaffirms_commitment_to_player_relief_efforts_with_2020_us_open_prize_money.html|archivedate=2020-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[多米尼克·蒂姆|多米尼克·蒂姆]]在男子单打决赛先丢两盘的情况下，连追三盘逆转击败[[亚历山大·兹韦列夫|亚历山大·兹韦列夫]]，成为历史上首位1990年后出生的大满贯男子单打冠军，以及历史上首位获得美网男单冠军的奥地利选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/tennis/2020/09/13/dominic-thiem-alexander-zverev-us-open-men-final/5788025002/|title=Dominic Thiem outlasts Alexander Zverev, comes back from two sets down to win US Open and first Grand Slam title|publisher=USA Today|date=2020-09-13|accessdate=2020-09-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226141922/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/tennis/2020/09/13/dominic-thiem-alexander-zverev-us-open-men-final/5788025002/|archivedate=2020-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。女子单打方面，[[大坂直美|大坂直美]]在决赛中以2比1的总比分击败第三次进入美网单打决赛的[[维多利亚·阿扎伦卡|维多利亚·阿扎伦卡]]，获得个人第二个美网冠军及第三个大满贯冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200913/k10012615261000.html|script-title=ja:大坂なおみ 全米オープン2回目の優勝 祝福や称賛の声|publisher=[[日本放送协会|NHK]]|date=2020-09-13|accessdate=2020-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913051911/https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200913/k10012615261000.html|archivedate=2020-09-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

